snippet.title: Amber Island by Nelward & HiP CoLouR - Vibes and Horns cover ft. Charlie Taylor
snippet.description:
Little cover I recorded over this awesome tune by HiP CoLouR, featuring my brother Charlie Taylor on the Tuba! 

Link to Charlie's channel:
https://youtube.com/channel/UC_G673CuWBFsHrUBGPiMnAw 

Follow me on insta and FB for more musical content!
https://www.instagram.com/alex.taylor.music/
https://www.facebook.com/alextaylor.vibesandhorns

And go check out HiP CoLouR too, his music is phenomenal!
https://www.instagram.com/hip_colour/
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zlCn-puwhvE
